{/* Introduction */}

About Me

Hi, I'm Manuel Lipo, a full-stack developer passionate about building modern, seamless web applications. With a deep understanding of both front-end and back-end technologies, I focus on delivering high-quality, user-centric solutions.

{/* Profile Picture */}

My Journey

From my early days customizing PC hardware as a teenager to mastering full-stack development, my journey has been driven by curiosity, a love for problem-solving, and continuous learning. Although I didn't finish university, I am self-taught and have built a solid foundation in web technologies like HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Ruby, Ruby on Rails, and PostgreSQL.
